<div class="c230_122">
<div id="v230.122.1"><span class="H7892 s">A Song</span><span class="H4609 s"> of degrees</span><span class="H1732 s"> of David</span><span class="H8055 s">. I was glad</span><span class="H559 s"> when they said</span><span class="H3212 s"> unto me, Let us go</span><span class="H1004 s"> into the house</span><span class="H3068 s"> of the LORD</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.122.2"><span class="H7272 s">Our feet</span><span class="H5975 s"> shall stand</span><span class="H8179 s"> within thy gates</span><span class="H3389 s">, O Jerusalem</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.122.3"><span class="H3389 s">Jerusalem</span><span class="H1129 s"> is builded</span><span class="H5892 s"> as a city</span><span class="H2266 s"> that is compact</span><span class="H3162 s"> together</span>:</div>
<div id="v230.122.4"><span class="H8033 s">Whither</span><span class="H7626 s"> the tribes</span><span class="H5927 s"> go up</span><span class="H7626 s">, the tribes</span><span class="H3050 s"> of the LORD</span><span class="H5715 s">, unto the testimony</span><span class="H3478 s"> of Israel</span><span class="H3034 s">, to give thanks</span><span class="H8034 s"> unto the name</span><span class="H3068 s"> of the LORD</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.122.5"><span class="H3427 s">For there are set</span><span class="H3678 s"> thrones</span><span class="H4941 s"> of judgment</span><span class="H3678 s">, the thrones</span><span class="H1004 s"> of the house</span><span class="H1732 s"> of David</span>. <span class="notes">Notes by the 1611 King James Bible Translators: (areâ€¦: Heb. do sit)</span></div>
<div id="v230.122.6"><span class="H7592 s">Pray</span><span class="H7965 s"> for the peace</span><span class="H3389 s"> of Jerusalem</span><span class="H7951 s">: they shall prosper</span><span class="H157 s"> that love</span> thee.</div>
<div id="v230.122.7"><span class="H7965 s">Peace</span><span class="H2426 s"> be within thy walls</span><span class="H7962 s">, <i>and</i> prosperity</span><span class="H759 s"> within thy palaces</span>.</div>
<div id="v230.122.8"><span class="H251 s">For my brethren</span><span class="H1696 s"> and companions' H7453 sakes, I will now say</span><span class="H7965 s">, Peace</span> <i>be</i> within thee.</div>
<div id="v230.122.9"><span class="H1004 s">Because of the house</span><span class="H3068 s"> of the LORD</span><span class="H430 s"> our God</span><span class="H1245 s"> I will seek</span><span class="H2896 s"> thy good</span>.</div></div>
